value.string: Just completed a total remodel by Ferrebbee Construction. All new kitchen and bathroom with leicht cabinets and granite counter tops. Living and dining has all new furniture from Latitudes and Minds Eye. Seeing is believing. No rental since remodel. Easy to show and open house every day. Best views of ocean and a light bright unit.

You will love the stunning ocean views from this great Kapalua oceanfront 2 bedroom, 3 bathroom condominium. Location, location, location. This precious single level property has arguably the best location at the Kapalua Bay Villas. Extremely popular vacation rental unit. Come see for yourself and you'll see why. Comfort at a higher level, it's a perfect home to relax and enjoy the best Kapalua Resort has to offer.

Enjoy the ocean all day long. Watch the changing colors over Molokai. Put your loung chair on the lawn right above the Blue Pacific Ocean and watch all of the whales and ocean movement. Great garden level unit and a nice light bright unit. Bay Villas have two tennis courts and three pools. Near 3 beaches and the great ocean front walk along the coastline. Kapalua resort has all of the golf and tennis you and your guests can enjoy or play on the Bay Villa courts also with your friends and neighbors in the resort. Enjoy the resort lifestyle and also a very quick walk to the spa each morning for all of your workout and pampering of self. Shuttle services to take you to all of the resort restaurants, golf courses and tennis courts.

Mesmerizing oceanfront location looking out to Molokai and North to Honolua Bay, this 1 bedroom, 2 bath unit is priced to sell. Enjoy this front row seat for whale watching, water action and all the color changes on Molokai all day long. There are only 6 units with this floor plan in the Bay Villas and this is the only one currently listed. This is the largest floor plan of the one bedroom single level units and is enhanced even more by the enclosure of the lanai adding additional living area to this already spacious unit. Flooring has been upgraded to tile throughout. Amenities of the Bay Villas include swimming pools, BBQ areas, tennis courts, on-site association office and direct beach access. Conveniently located within walking distance to the Kapalua Spa, hiking trails, award winning Resort restaurants and the Kapalua Bay Golf Course.

Located in a world class development with golf courses, restaurants, beaches, hotels and more. Gorgeous direct ocean view unit overlooking the pool and the pathway to the ocean. You could probably see whales in the winter from your own lanai. Tenant occupied, 48 hrs notice for all showings. Price slashed to $725,000 for quick sale!

EXTRAORDINARY. MAUI. Bay Villa 31B3,4 is a tastefully remodeled and furnished two bedroom, three bathroom townhouse villa with superb ocean and outer island views. The villa was remodeled in 2007 to the gold villa standards of The Kapalua Villas rental program and exudes a luxury resort lifestyle in every detail. The Bay Villas shoreline community features 141 villas in 27 buildings on approximately 16.5 acres in the heart of the Kapalua resort. Amenities include 3 swimming pools, recreation and barbecue areas, tennis courts, coastal walking trails, and access to nearby golf, hotels, restaurants, and spas. Located on Maui’s northwest shore, the Kapalua Resort stretches from emerald mountain peaks to the edge of the glistening Pacific Ocean. A 23,000 acre natural paradise unfolds, featuring award winning accommodations, premier Maui real estate, two world class golf courses, unspoiled beaches, misty mountains, ancient lava flows and fields of lush greenery. We invite you to make Kapalua your home.

This is a great opportunity to own a two bedroom Bay Villa ocean front villa at a fantastic new price! Ocean front locations are in demand and this one is priced to be one of the best two bedroom values on the resort, so don’t wait! The exterior of building 28 has been upgraded and painted in December 2012. Guests will enjoy the quality and location, and owners will appreciate and value the outstanding rental history and Kapalua lifestyle. Remodeled in 2006, features include stone floors, granite countertops, updated kitchen and baths, and a re-designed staircase that provides for additional owner storage. The downstairs guest room and bath is wheelchair accessible, giving this villa flexibility in use and design. The arrival to the villa is via a bridge level, providing easy access for you and your guests. The Bay Villas community amenities include shoreline, beach and coastal trail access, three swimming pools, tennis courts and covered recreation/barbecue areas. Located on Maui's northwest shore nine miles from the historic town of Lahaina, the Kapalua Resort stretches from emerald mountain peaks to the edge of the glistening Pacific Ocean. A 23,000-acre natural paradise unfolds, featuring award-winning accommodations and restaurants, premier Maui real estate, spa, world-class golf courses, unspoiled beaches and dramatic scenery. The blue waters of the Pacific are the winter breeding grounds for the majestic Humpback whales.

Offering one of the finest 2-bedroom, 3-bathroom properties in the Kapalua Bay Villas, this property is one of the reasons why YOU keep coming back to Maui! This 1,529 square foot property was fully renovated by Maui's own Koliana Designs. Words failed to describe its beauty and location. Sold fully furnished and turn-key. Kapalua Bay Villas is an oceanfront condominium community of 141 apartments in twenty-seven 1-story and 2-story buildings. The community is spread across 16.451 acres and offers pools & tennis court. Beach front access to Kapalua Bay and Oneloa Bay is within walking distance from this oceanfront condominium community. YOUR Time is Now.

EXTRAORDINARY. MAUI. Perched overlooking the white sandy beach at Oneloa Bay, this spectacular two bedroom villa offers incredible ocean views from the living room, dining, kitchen, and both bedrooms. Beautifully renovated, Bay Villa 20G1-3 features a chef’s kitchen with custom cabinetry and top of the line appliances. With ample outdoor lanai space, the living room and master bathroom lanais were enclosed to create larger living spaces that capture the spectacular ocean and mountain views. Offered furnished, this is a spectacular home base to enjoy all of the amenities of the Kapalua Resort: beaches, world class golf, tennis, hiking and coastal trails, and fantastic restaurants.

Maui oceanfront living at its best. Beautiful remodeled "gold standard" end townhouse with travertine flooring downstairs and excellent granite counter tops. Cherry cabinets with cherry panel accents for a more home feel. Top quality throughout. Wonderful ocean views from the upstairs bedroom and very nice views from the living area with a great lawn out to the ocean and rocks.. Bay Villas have 3 pools and this unit is very near a pool with barbecue and also near the oceanfront walk to Kapalua Bay and beach. Bay Villas have two tennis courts for owners enjoyment. This is a great opportunity to have a home on the oceanfront with big outdoor lanai downstairs and very nice lanai upstairs off the bedroom for more sunbathing. Upstairs bathroom has a nice big shower with two shower heads and double sink. Begin your Maui lifestyle here. A/c also.

Great Location! Fantastic Ocean Views! Street level entrance townhouse floor plan so upstairs bedroom has the same unbelievable ocean and Molokai view as the living room. Updated kitchen with new cabinets, granite counters and top of the line appliances. Downstairs lanai has been enclosed to increase the living room area. The upstairs loft bedroom floor has been extended to create a very large bedroom suite with outside lanai.

Location, Location, Location.....this stunning townhouse has one of the best, premier oceanfront locations at the famed Kapalua Bay Villa Resort. Expanded and renovated with high end decorative finishes and striking custom furnishings, this villa has stellar oceanfront views from every vantage point, allowing you to take in the beauty of the Kapalua coastline. Wake up each morning to the sound and beauty of the ocean as you enjoy private unparalleled views from the spacious oceanfront master suite. As the sun sets, gaze from your private lanai at the captivating evening lights of the resort, at the edge of the glistening ocean. Offered beautifully furnished, this centrally located villa is the perfect home base to enjoy the lifestyle and amenities of the Kapalua Resort. This villa is in a private rental program with a strong, high occupancy, for those seeking not only a great home, but a history of solid income.

Highly desirable bridge level location at the Bay Villas, a prime Kapalua oceanfront development. This newly upgraded single-level condominium offers spectacular ocean views. In like-new condition, featuring granite counter tops in the kitchen and bath and new state-of-the-art appliances. Offered turnkey with new furnishings and interior design. Bay Villa & Kapalua Resort amenities include two world class golf courses, the Kapalua Spa, shuttle services throughout the resort, two tennis courts, three swimming pools, recreation areas with bbqs and direct access to beautiful white sand beaches just steps away. Located adjacent to Kapalua Place – a gated residential enclave with estates valued in the $10-$20 million range.

EXTRAORDINARY. MAUI. Just steps to the white sand beach at Oneloa Bay, this oceanfront villa has been renovated to the Gold Standard, with new cabinetry, granite top of the line appliances, and designer furnishings with an elegant, tropical flare. Building 22 is considered to be one of the best locations at the Bay Villas. Oriented toward Molokai, the lanai is sheltered from the prevailing tradewinds, and is situated oceanfront with no other buildings in the view plane. The Bay Villas are centrally located within the Kapalua Resort – close to beaches, golf, tennis, walking trails, the Kapalua spa and the resort’s many restaurants.

Oceanfront location in Kapalua Bay Villas. "Gold Standard" in Outrigger program. Incredible bridge style townhouse unit. Shower in downstairs bathroom. Completely remodeled. Private master suite. Easy walk to Kapalua or Oneloa Bay. The Kapalua Nature Trail and sea bird preserve are directly in front of 36B3. 2 tennis courts, 3 pools, resort shuttle service, resort security, Kapalua spa, 2 world class golf courses, great restaurants all the amenities one would expect from a world renowned resort. Sold furnished. Original artwork not included in the sale.

Kapalua's most prestigious beachfront location - Coconut Grove on Kapalua Bay. A gated community of only 36 condominium residences, Coconut Grove 29's prime location offers fabulous ocean, island and sunset views. This spacious ground level floor plan includes an interior courtyard of almost 700 square feet offering total privacy. The courtyard is tiled and landscaped completing a perfect setting for outdoor entertaining. Offered unfurnished.

This is a must see oceanfront unit with fantastic ocean views. Watch the whales and the dolphins and all the cruise ships go by. Oneloa Beach is steps away. Pool is steps away. Bridge level for easy convenient access. Unit has a great bathroom with tub and also a separate shower and also a water feature that is turned off during rentals. Kitchen and all has been upgraded also with all new cabinets and granite counter tops. Appliances were all new. Bay villas have 3 pools, near Kapalua beach, have their own tennis courts and office. Great oceanfront beachwalk for your daily exercise. Kapalua has restaurants and a spa as well as tennis and golf managed by Troon.

One of the best locations at Kapalua Bay Villas! For an amazing price. Panoramic ocean views from this spectacular villa! Bridge level loft with two enclosed lanais. Current Title issues with this unit have been resolved and is clean.

From the moment you enter Kapalua Bay Villa # 32B3 you will be captivated by the gorgeous sweeping panoramic Pacific Ocean views. You will appreciate the stylish and comfortable furnishings of this remodeled second floor "bridge" level, townhouse style, one bedroom, one and a half bath condominium. Proudly offered and remodeled to the "Kapalua Gold Villa" standard. The living room balcony "lanai" enclosure allows for additional interior space while creating a serene place to enjoy ocean views and whale watching in season. The updated kitchen is both functional and polished with it's cabinetry and granite countertops. The half bath "powder room" is conveniently located off the kitchen. Breathtaking views continue as you enter the tastefully decorated bedroom appropriate for an upscale Kapalua, Maui property. The bedroom features a private balcony "lanai", which is another great vantage point for enjoying the view and ocean breezes. A spacious full bathroom off the bedroom is complete with sunken tub and, shower and granite countertop. Bosch brand washer and dryer are conveniently located outside the upstairs bathroom. With the remodeling complete and an attractive list price, this beautiful property is ready to embrace a new owner. The beauty and amenities of the Kapalua resort and all the comforts of this condo are here to welcome you "E Komo Mai".
